<text><body>
<lb n="0217b04" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0217b05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0217b06" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1089</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0217b07" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0217001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享和年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】平安時代寫東寺三密藏本</note>都表如意摩尼轉輪聖王次第念
<lb n="0217b08" ed="T"/>誦祕密最要略法</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0217b09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0217b10" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0217002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔解脫師子譯〕－【甲】</note><note n="0217002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">解脫師子譯【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0217002"><lem wit="【大】">解脫師子譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0217b11" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="1" type="品">1 相貌品</cb:mulu><head>相貌品第一</head>
<lb n="0217b12" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0217b1201"><l>我今當說思惟<note n="0217003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＝寶ヵ【原】</note><note n="0217003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，寶【考偽-原】</note><app n="0217003"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">寶</rdg></app></l><l>三種真言而次第</l>
<lb n="0217b13" ed="T"/><l>初用大心外加持</l><l>第二根本復想內</l>
<lb n="0217b14" ed="T"/><l>第三小心內外通</l><l>應可存心無錯亂</l>
<lb n="0217b15" ed="T"/><l>如是三道妙真言</l><l>安立行者明王地</l>
<lb n="0217b16" ed="T"/><l>若有修此三昧耶</l><l>須具七種殊勝相</l>
<lb n="0217b17" ed="T"/><l>猶如輪王持七寶</l><l>王四天下皆降伏</l>
<lb n="0217b18" ed="T"/><l>次說順諸念誦法</l><l>復擇<note n="0217004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">清淨吉祥＝淨吉祥之【甲】</note><note n="0217004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">清淨吉祥【大】，淨吉祥之【甲】</note><app n="0217004"><lem wit="【大】">清淨吉祥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">淨吉祥之</rdg></app>地</l>
<lb n="0217b19" ed="T"/><l>或在山間及池邊</l><l>或在伽藍精室處</l>
<lb n="0217b20" ed="T"/><l>或<note n="0217005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛＝神ィ【原】</note><note n="0217005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，神【校異-原】</note><app n="0217005"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">神</rdg></app>舍利神塔中</l><l>應可存心辦諸俱</l>
<lb n="0217b21" ed="T"/><l>先以持地如教命</l><l><note n="0217006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">復次＝次復【甲】</note><note n="0217006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復次【大】，次復【甲】</note><app n="0217006"><lem wit="【大】">復次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">次復</rdg></app>安置本尊者</l>
<lb n="0217b22" ed="T"/><l>行者自須敷已座</l><l>尊面西方在目前</l>
<lb n="0217b23" ed="T"/><l>行者像前面東坐</l><l>清淨沐浴香塗身</l>
<lb n="0217b24" ed="T"/><l>兼著新淨妙衣服</l><l>又持種種供養具</l>
<lb n="0217b25" ed="T"/><l>步步想<note n="0217007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">八＝成【甲】</note><note n="0217007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八【大】，成【甲】</note><app n="0217007"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">成</rdg></app>葉蓮華</l><l>存想變地無濁穢</l>
<lb n="0217b26" ed="T"/><l>加持護身入精室</l><l>安置像前而念誦</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0217b27" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="2" type="品">2 大心密言品</cb:mulu><head>大心密言品第二</head>
<lb n="0217b28" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0217b2801"><l>先用大心真言王</l><l>澡浴洗淨結護法</l>
<lb n="0217b29" ed="T"/><l>呪水灑身加持衣</l><l>復須想念皆成就</l>
<pb n="0217c" xml:id="T20.1089.0217c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0217c01" ed="T"/><l>如此五種隨次第</l><l>都用大明及本印</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0217c0201" cb:type="dharani">唵波怛摩進跢末尼摩賀惹嚩<note place="inline">引</note>囉吽</p>
<lb n="0217c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0217c0301">澡豆沐浴之具。各呪七遍。然後澡洗。</p>
<lb n="0217c04" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0217c0401"><l>想水白色</l><l>猶如甘露</l><l>又<note n="0217008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">想自＝自想【甲】</note><note n="0217008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">想自【大】，自想【甲】</note><app n="0217008"><lem wit="【大】">想自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">自想</rdg></app>身</l>
<lb n="0217c05" ed="T"/><l>垢穢煩惱</l><l>受此水已</l><l>一切塵勞</l>
<lb n="0217c06" ed="T"/><l>皆悉<note n="0217009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔落〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0217009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">落【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0217009"><lem wit="【大】">落</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>盡</l><l>洗浴畢已</l><l>應須洗淨</l>
<lb n="0217c07" ed="T"/><l><note n="0217010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">取＝聚ィ【原】</note><note n="0217010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取【大】，聚【校異-原】</note><app n="0217010"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">聚</rdg></app>土少許</l><l>加持七遍</l><l>隨時洗淨</l>
<lb n="0217c08" ed="T"/><l>然後著衣</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0217c0901">時其衣亦復加持七遍作如此想。</p>
<lb n="0217c10" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0217c1001"><l>我今此身</l><l>被金剛甲</l><l>依法<note n="0217011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訖＝詑ィ【原】</note><note n="0217011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訖【大】，詑【校異-原】</note><app n="0217011"><lem wit="【大】">訖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">詑</rdg></app>已</l>
<lb n="0217c11" ed="T"/><l>即須灑身</l><l>用水一掬</l><l>加持七遍</l>
<lb n="0217c12" ed="T"/><l>散灑其身</l><l>想虛空中</l><l>雨諸寶華</l>
<lb n="0217c13" ed="T"/><l>遍滿世界</l><l><note n="0217012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＝使【甲】</note><note n="0217012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，使【甲】</note><app n="0217012"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">使</rdg></app>須護身</l><l>結此密印</l>
<lb n="0217c14" ed="T"/><l>誦持七遍</l><l>印於七處</l><l>心及兩肩</l>
<lb n="0217c15" ed="T"/><l>兩<note n="0217013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眼＝胸ィ【原】</note><note n="0217013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眼【大】，胸【校異-原】</note><app n="0217013"><lem wit="【大】">眼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">胸</rdg></app>兩膝</l><l>散於頭上</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0217c1601"><note n="0217014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亦＝二ィ【原】</note><note n="0217014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亦【大】，二【校異-原】</note><app n="0217014"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">二</rdg></app>成大護身已。即須結界。</p>
<lb n="0217c17" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0217c1701"><l>若結壇界</l><l>開於四門</l><l>不應結界</l>
<lb n="0217c18" ed="T"/><l>若作結護</l><l>皆須用心</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0217c1901">亦鋪置次第即作啟請等<note n="0217015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">事＝畢ィ【原】</note><note n="0217015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事【大】，畢【校異-原】</note><app n="0217015"><lem wit="【大】">事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">畢</rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0217c20" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="3" type="品">3 根本密言品</cb:mulu><head>根本密言品第三</head>
<lb n="0217c21" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0217c2101"><l>復說根本軌儀法</l><l>想念奉請大聖王</l>
<lb n="0217c22" ed="T"/><l>誦此密言及結印</l><l>一一自<note n="0217016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">想＝須【甲】</note><note n="0217016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">想【大】，須【甲】</note><app n="0217016"><lem wit="【大】">想</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">須</rdg></app>往彼山</l>
<lb n="0217c23" ed="T"/><l>存心頂禮而奉請</l><l>迎引尊者入道場</l>
<lb n="0217c24" ed="T"/><l>復用遏伽而授與</l><l>香華飲食及塗<note n="0217017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">香＝身ィ【原】</note><note n="0217017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">香【大】，身【校異-原】</note><app n="0217017"><lem wit="【大】">香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">身</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0217c25" ed="T"/><l>燈蓋幢幡兼藥等</l><l>如法供養彼明王</l>
<lb n="0217c26" ed="T"/><l>想念供養尊者已</l><l>隨便持珠誦密言</l>
<lb n="0217c27" ed="T"/><l>悔<note n="0217018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">先世過＝過先世【甲】</note><note n="0217018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">先世過【大】，過先世【甲】</note><app n="0217018"><lem wit="【大】">先世過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">過先世</rdg></app>及發願</l><l>至誠端坐觀明王</l></lg>
<lb n="0217c28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0217c2801">行者像前端坐思惟。存心諦觀布多勒伽山
<lb n="0217c29" ed="T"/>眾寶莊嚴華果茂盛。</p>
<pb n="0218a" xml:id="T20.1089.0218a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0218a01" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0218a0101"><l>其山頂上</l><l>聖者宮殿</l><l>本在其中</l>
<lb n="0218a02" ed="T"/><l>應想聖者</l><l>安坐殿中</l><l>殊妙供具</l>
<lb n="0218a03" ed="T"/><l>莊嚴其身</l><l>行者於此</l><l>心想之中</l>
<lb n="0218a04" ed="T"/><l>自往彼山</l><l>迎<note n="0218001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誦＝請【甲】</note><note n="0218001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦【大】，請【甲】</note><app n="0218001"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">請</rdg></app>尊者</l><l>引入道場</l>
<lb n="0218a05" ed="T"/><l>於壇中心</l><l>蓮華臺上</l><l>安置聖者</l></lg>
<lb n="0218a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218a0601">次奉遏伽水。</p>
<lb n="0218a07" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0218a0701"><l>於新銅器</l><l>或用白瓷</l><l>器盛香水</l>
<lb n="0218a08" ed="T"/><l>奉於聖者</l><l>便誦真言</l><l>復想此水</l>
<lb n="0218a09" ed="T"/><l>聖者受已</l><l>遍灑四方</l><l>及灑妙身</l></lg>
<lb n="0218a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218a1001">行者細觀尊灑水已。三千大千世界猶如瑠
<lb n="0218a11" ed="T"/>璃內外明徹中無一物。</p>
<lb n="0218a12" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0218a1201"><l><note n="0218002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">奉＋（請）【明】</note><note n="0218002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉【大】，奉請【明】</note><app n="0218002"><lem wit="【大】">奉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">奉請</rdg></app>遏伽已</l><l>次復供養</l><l>香華飲食</l>
<lb n="0218a13" ed="T"/><l>塗香末香</l><l>燈蓋之事</l><l>一一加持</l>
<lb n="0218a14" ed="T"/><l>真言及印</l></lg>
<lb n="0218a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218a1501">供<note n="0218003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">養＋（事）ィ【原】</note><note n="0218003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">養【大】，養事【校異-原】</note><app n="0218003"><lem wit="【大】">養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">養事</rdg></app>畢已。於本尊聖者前悔謝其身<note n="0218004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呵＝可【甲】</note><note n="0218004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呵【大】，可【甲】</note><app n="0218004"><lem wit="【大】">呵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">可</rdg></app>責
<lb n="0218a16" ed="T"/>己過。</p>
<lb n="0218a17" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0218a1701"><l><note n="0218005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔次〕－【甲】</note><note n="0218005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0218005"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>復發願</l><l>隨心所求</l><l>悉皆陳說</l>
<lb n="0218a18" ed="T"/><l>於其想中</l><l>結壇三門</l><l>唯留西門</l>
<lb n="0218a19" ed="T"/><l>復結大界</l><l>身外四方</l><l>周匝鋪置</l>
<lb n="0218a20" ed="T"/><l>及虛空界</l><l>次用塗香</l><l>塗手臂<note n="0218006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔上〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0218006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0218006"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0218a21" ed="T"/><l>然後<note n="0218007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">念＋（珠）【甲】</note><note n="0218007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念【大】，念珠【甲】</note><app n="0218007"><lem wit="【大】">念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">念珠</rdg></app>誦</l></lg>
<lb n="0218a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218a2201">執念珠以<note n="0218008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">珠熏香＝珍重心【甲】</note><note n="0218008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">珠熏香【大】，珍重心【甲】</note><app n="0218008"><lem wit="【大】">珠熏香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">珍重心</rdg></app>。二手合掌再三頂戴作如
<lb n="0218a23" ed="T"/>是言。</p>
<lb n="0218a24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0218a2401"><l><note n="0218009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我念存＝作珍重ィ【原】，我今存【甲】</note><note n="0218009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我念存【大】，作珍重【校異-原】，我今存【甲】</note><app n="0218009"><lem wit="【大】">我念存</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">作珍重</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">我今存</rdg></app>心</l><l>承事聖者</l><l>持此密言</l>
<lb n="0218a25" ed="T"/><l>唯願尊者</l><l>不<note n="0218010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捨大＝捻大慈【甲】</note><note n="0218010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捨大【大】，捻大慈【甲】</note><app n="0218010"><lem wit="【大】">捨大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">捻大慈</rdg></app>悲</l><l>莫違本誓</l>
<lb n="0218a26" ed="T"/><l>發弘誓願</l><l>速現一切</l><l>妙莊嚴身</l>
<lb n="0218a27" ed="T"/><l>我若見已</l><l>現身即得</l><l>證法雲地</l>
<lb n="0218a28" ed="T"/><l>常侍尊者</l><l>不離左右</l><l>發此願已</l>
<lb n="0218a29" ed="T"/><l>便誦根本</l><l>祕密真言曰</l></lg>
<pb n="0218b" xml:id="T20.1089.0218b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0218b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218b0101" cb:type="dharani">曩<note place="inline">上</note>謨<note n="0218011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0218011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0218011"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>阿<note place="inline">去引</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">上二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline"><note n="0218012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">長＝去ィ【原】</note><note n="0218012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">長【大】，去【校異-原】</note><app n="0218012"><lem wit="【大】">長</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">去</rdg></app>引</note>
<lb n="0218b02" ed="T"/>野<note place="inline">一</note>曩<note n="0218013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔上〕－【甲】</note><note n="0218013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0218013"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>莫阿<note place="inline">去</note>哩野<note place="inline">二合<anchor xml:id="fxT20p0218b01"/>引</note><note n="0218014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚩＝縛【甲】＊</note><note n="0218014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】＊，縛【甲】＊</note><app n="0218014"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>路枳帝<note place="inline">三</note>濕
<lb n="0218b03" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0218014"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>囉野<note place="inline">四</note>冒地薩怛嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>野<note place="inline">五</note>摩賀薩怛
<lb n="0218b04" ed="T"/>嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>野<note place="inline">六</note>摩賀迦<note place="inline">去</note>嚕抳<note place="inline">去</note>迦<note place="inline">去</note>野<note place="inline">七</note>怛儞野<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0218b05" ed="T"/>合</note>他<note place="inline">去八</note>唵<note place="inline">九</note>左訖囉<note place="inline">二合</note>嚩底<note place="inline">十</note>進跢末抳<note place="inline">去十一</note>
<lb n="0218b06" ed="T"/>摩<note n="0218015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＝賀【甲】</note><note n="0218015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】，賀【甲】</note><app n="0218015"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賀</rdg></app>跛納冥<note place="inline">二合十二</note>嚕嚕底瑟吒<note place="inline">二合十三</note>入嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>囉
<lb n="0218b07" ed="T"/><note place="inline">十四</note>阿訖羅灑<note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">十五</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>泮吒<note place="inline">十六</note>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合
<lb n="0218b08" ed="T"/>引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0218b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218b0901">誦此真言。於七日中滿三十萬遍。聖者即現
<lb n="0218b10" ed="T"/>持誦人前。隨心所求皆得成就。</p>
<lb n="0218b11" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0218b1101"><l>若常持<note n="0218016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">念＝誦【甲】</note><note n="0218016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念【大】，誦【甲】</note><app n="0218016"><lem wit="【大】">念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">誦</rdg></app></l><l>每日三時</l><l>時別念誦</l>
<lb n="0218b12" ed="T"/><l>一千八遍</l><l>或<note n="0218017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">百八＝八百【甲】＊</note><note n="0218017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">百八【大】＊，八百【甲】＊</note><app n="0218017"><lem wit="【大】">百八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">八百</rdg></app>遍</l><l>如是數滿</l>
<lb n="0218b13" ed="T"/><l>三十萬遍</l><l>即成悉地</l><l>時別皆作</l>
<lb n="0218b14" ed="T"/><l>迎送之事</l><l>付<note n="0218018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囑＝屬【甲】＊</note><note n="0218018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囑【大】＊，屬【甲】＊</note><app n="0218018"><lem wit="【大】">囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app>等法</l></lg>
<lb n="0218b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218b1501">大心密言曰。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0218b1506" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">唵嚩<note n="0218019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉曩＝囉ィ【原】，曩【甲】</note><note n="0218019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉曩【大】，囉【校異-原】，曩【甲】</note><app n="0218019"><lem wit="【大】">囉曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">囉</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">曩</rdg></app><note place="inline">上</note>娜跛納冥<note place="inline">二合</note>進
<lb n="0218b16" ed="T"/>跢末尼<note place="inline">上</note>摩賀入嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>囉吽<note place="inline">引</note>泮吒娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0218b17" ed="T"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p></cb:div>
<lb n="0218b18" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="4" type="品">4 小心密言品</cb:mulu><head>小心密言品第四</head>
<lb n="0218b19" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0218b1901"><l>復說最勝小心王</l><l>能成一切諸悉地</l>
<lb n="0218b20" ed="T"/><l>三業齊用結妙印</l><l>誦祕真言而付<app type="star" corresp="#0218018"><lem wit="【大】">囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0218b21" ed="T"/><l>又於想中除結界</l><l>次奉遏伽灑四方</l>
<lb n="0218b22" ed="T"/><l><note n="0218020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">後＝復【甲】</note><note n="0218020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">後【大】，復【甲】</note><app n="0218020"><lem wit="【大】">後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>責已過<note n="0218021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">深＝除【甲】</note><note n="0218021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">深【大】，除【甲】</note><app n="0218021"><lem wit="【大】">深</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">除</rdg></app>慚愧</l><l>引<note n="0218022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝入ィ【原】</note><note n="0218022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，入【校異-原】</note><app n="0218022"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">入</rdg></app>聖者還本宮</l>
<lb n="0218b23" ed="T"/><l>安置尊者彼殿已</l><l>辭別自念還本<note n="0218023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">方＝宮【甲】</note><note n="0218023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">方【大】，宮【甲】</note><app n="0218023"><lem wit="【大】">方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">宮</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0218b24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0218b2401"><l>又復行者</l><l>每持誦已</l><l>須作付<app type="star" corresp="#0218018"><lem wit="【大】">囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0218b25" ed="T"/><l>結此密印</l><l>及誦真言</l><l>付<app type="star" corresp="#0218018"><lem wit="【大】">囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app>聖者</l>
<lb n="0218b26" ed="T"/><l>作如是語</l><l>所有遍數</l><l>及持功夫</l>
<lb n="0218b27" ed="T"/><l>付<app type="star" corresp="#0218018"><lem wit="【大】">囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app>尊者</l><l>唯願尊<note n="0218024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0218024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0218024"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></l><l>受取守護</l>
<lb n="0218b28" ed="T"/><l>莫令散失</l><l>又想手印</l><l>猶如寶藏</l>
<lb n="0218b29" ed="T"/><l>一切遍數</l><l>安在藏中</l><l>授與聖者</l>
<pb n="0218c" xml:id="T20.1089.0218c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0218c01" ed="T"/><l>聖者受已</l><l>置蓮華中</l><l><note n="0218025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔作〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0218025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">作【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0218025"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>付<app type="star" corresp="#0218018"><lem wit="【大】">囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app>畢</l>
<lb n="0218c02" ed="T"/><l>亦須悔過</l><l>發弘誓願</l><l>然後<note n="0218026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔復〕－【甲】</note><note n="0218026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0218026"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>作</l>
<lb n="0218c03" ed="T"/><l>聖者還宮</l><l>引送之法</l><l>即除結界</l>
<lb n="0218c04" ed="T"/><l>復取香水</l><l>散灑四方</l><l>及奉聖者</l>
<lb n="0218c05" ed="T"/><l>便當引送</l><l>復<note n="0218027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔結〕－【甲】</note><note n="0218027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">結【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0218027"><lem wit="【大】">結</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>密印</l><l><note n="0218028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔及〕－【甲】</note><note n="0218028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0218028"><lem wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>誦真言</l>
<lb n="0218c06" ed="T"/><l>又想自身</l><l>還送聖者</l><l>至於本宮</l>
<lb n="0218c07" ed="T"/><l>安置殿中</l><l>聖者坐已</l><l>自須辭去</l>
<lb n="0218c08" ed="T"/><l>却還本方</l></lg>
<lb n="0218c09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218c0901">小心密言曰。</p><p xml:id="pT20p0218c0906" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">唵嚩<note place="inline">引</note>囉娜跛納冥<note n="0218029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><note n="0218029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0218029"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0218c10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218c1001">此中<note n="0218030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">密＝或【甲】</note><note n="0218030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">密【大】，或【甲】</note><app n="0218030"><lem wit="【大】">密</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">或</rdg></app>印相貌我今說之。初作大印用種種
<lb n="0218c11" ed="T"/>塗香塗於手<note n="0218031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔臂〕－【甲】</note><note n="0218031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臂【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0218031"><lem wit="【大】">臂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。然後結印頂戴當心合掌。二
<lb n="0218c12" ed="T"/>小指及無名指。鉤在掌中。其二頭指押中指
<lb n="0218c13" ed="T"/>背第二節上。二大指並竪。</p>
<lb n="0218c14" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0218c1401"><l>此是大心</l><l>真言密印</l><l>要須共用</l>
<lb n="0218c15" ed="T"/><l>所作加持</l><l>其祕密言</l><l>各誦七遍</l>
<lb n="0218c16" ed="T"/><l>各印印之</l><l>或擲或止</l><l>要當想成</l>
<lb n="0218c17" ed="T"/><l>一一如法</l><l>不得就中</l><l>心緣餘境</l>
<lb n="0218c18" ed="T"/><l>隨順世法</l><l>行住坐臥</l><l>安在諸佛</l>
<lb n="0218c19" ed="T"/><l>甚深境界</l><l>若有行者</l><l>修此法<app type="star" corresp="#0218024"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0218c20" ed="T"/><l>不久即成</l><l>一切種智</l></lg>
<lb n="0218c21" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" n="1" type="其他">第二根本真言印</cb:mulu><head>第二根本真言印</head>
<lb n="0218c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218c2201">以二手腕相著。當在胸前。其十指並散。二小
<lb n="0218c23" ed="T"/>指及二大指並竪猶如蓮花形。亦依前法印
<lb n="0218c24" ed="T"/>之止之。惟有迎請母指來去。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0218c25" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" n="2" type="其他">第三小心真言印</cb:mulu><head><note n="0218032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔第三…印〕七字－【甲】</note><note n="0218032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（第三…印）七字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="7" n="0218032"><lem wit="【大】">第三小心真言印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></head>
<lb n="0218c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0218c2601"><note n="0218033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（印）ィ＋以【原】</note><note n="0218033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，印以【校異-原】</note><app n="0218033"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">印以</rdg></app>二手虛心合掌猶如未開蓮花。若付<app type="star" corresp="#0218018"><lem wit="【大】">囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屬</rdg></app>
<lb n="0218c27" ed="T"/>時依前想念。發遣尊者開二大指。此小心<note n="0218034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">密印＝印密【甲】</note><note n="0218034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">密印【大】，印密【甲】</note><app n="0218034"><lem wit="【大】">密
<lb n="0218c28" ed="T"/>印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">印密</rdg></app>通蓮花部一切處用。我今於大蓮花部三
<lb n="0218c29" ed="T"/>昧耶中略出<note n="0218035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＋（法）ィ【原】</note><note n="0218035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此【大】，此法【校異-原】</note><app n="0218035"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">此法</rdg></app>祕密甚深<note n="0218036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔念誦〕－【甲】</note><note n="0218036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念誦【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0218036"><lem wit="【大】">念誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>次第。其修
<pb n="0219a" xml:id="T20.1089.0219a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0219a01" ed="T"/>行者不得錯傳如護眼目。若能如是。一切聖
<lb n="0219a02" ed="T"/>者皆大歡喜憶念此人。一切善神日夜常護
<lb n="0219a03" ed="T"/>不離左右。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb n="0219a04" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="5" type="品">5 成就世間出世間除災護摩念誦品</cb:mulu><head>成就世間出世間除災護摩念誦品第五</head>
<lb n="0219a05" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0219a0501"><l>我今順於蓮花部</l><l>略說如意摩尼輪</l>
<lb n="0219a06" ed="T"/><l>能勝諸部最祕密</l><l>成就世法出世<note n="0219001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＝間ィ【原】，門【甲】</note><note n="0219001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，間【校異-原】，門【甲】</note><app n="0219001"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">間</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">門</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219a07" ed="T"/><l>念誦都有四種<note n="0219002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">相＝法ィ【原】</note><note n="0219002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，法【校異-原】</note><app n="0219002"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">法</rdg></app></l><l>行者諦聽我說之</l>
<lb n="0219a08" ed="T"/><l>初作息災加持法</l><l>第二增益福智成</l>
<lb n="0219a09" ed="T"/><l>第三隨心愛念法</l><l>第四降伏一切<note n="0219003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怨＝惡ィ【原】</note><note n="0219003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怨【大】，惡【校異-原】</note><app n="0219003"><lem wit="【大】">怨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">惡</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219a10" ed="T"/><l>此四種持<note n="0219004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">護摩事＝誦護摩ィ【原】</note><note n="0219004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">護摩事【大】，誦護摩【校異-原】</note><app n="0219004"><lem wit="【大】">護摩事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">誦護摩</rdg></app></l><l>上中下法次第陳</l>
<lb n="0219a11" ed="T"/><l>若欲成就息災者</l><l>先發安忍慈悲心</l>
<lb n="0219a12" ed="T"/><l>須求無上妙覺地</l><l><note n="0219005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">莫＝真【甲】</note><note n="0219005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莫【大】，真【甲】</note><app n="0219005"><lem wit="【大】">莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">真</rdg></app>樂聲聞二乘心</l>
<lb n="0219a13" ed="T"/><l>復若<note n="0219006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">求成就＝成就求【甲】</note><note n="0219006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">求成就【大】，成就求【甲】</note><app n="0219006"><lem wit="【大】">求成就</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">成就求</rdg></app>大事</l><l>要當先作轉障法</l>
<lb n="0219a14" ed="T"/><l>又取白檀十六指</l><l>一持一燒稱<note n="0219007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">己＝所【甲】</note><note n="0219007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">己【大】，所【甲】</note><app n="0219007"><lem wit="【大】">己</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">所</rdg></app>名</l>
<lb n="0219a15" ed="T"/><l>數至<app type="star" corresp="#0218017"><lem wit="【大】">百八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">八百</rdg></app>或千八</l><l>本所求願皆滿足</l>
<lb n="0219a16" ed="T"/><l>行者若除他病時</l><l><note n="0219008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔或滅…厄〕七字－【甲】</note><note n="0219008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（或滅…厄）七字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="7" n="0219008"><lem wit="【大】">或滅國中大災厄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219a17" ed="T"/><l>或自他災及畜生</l><l>應可存心請大聖</l>
<lb n="0219a18" ed="T"/><l>於其一一大城門</l><l>想中各安本尊者</l>
<lb n="0219a19" ed="T"/><l>種種殊妙寶莊嚴</l><l>思惟六臂如<note n="0219009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">盡＝畫ィ【原】</note><note n="0219009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡【大】，畫【校異-原】</note><app n="0219009"><lem wit="【大】">盡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">畫</rdg></app>說</l>
<lb n="0219a20" ed="T"/><l>又想眉間出白光</l><l>徐徐廣引遍世界</l>
<lb n="0219a21" ed="T"/><l>一切眾生所有殃</l><l>悉皆頓謝無所有</l>
<lb n="0219a22" ed="T"/><l>或想此光入我身</l><l>一切罪障皆滅盡</l>
<lb n="0219a23" ed="T"/><l>罪滅福生以加持</l><l>復勤念誦便成就</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0219a24" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="6" type="品">6 增益福德品</cb:mulu><head>增益福德品第六</head>
<lb n="0219a25" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0219a2501"><l>我今略說福生法</l><l>大慈悲故順有情</l>
<lb n="0219a26" ed="T"/><l>菩薩分身遍一切</l><l>隨彼眾生所樂心</l>
<lb n="0219a27" ed="T"/><l>又復安立諸珍藏</l><l>種種法門各不同</l>
<lb n="0219a28" ed="T"/><l>百千萬國所隨者</l><l>一一勤求皆悉成</l>
<lb n="0219a29" ed="T"/><l>或說相法或無相</l><l>隨順眾生性所趣</l>
<pb n="0219b" xml:id="T20.1089.0219b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0219b01" ed="T"/><l>建立佛<note n="0219010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＝性【甲】</note><note n="0219010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，性【甲】</note><app n="0219010"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">性</rdg></app>護世界</l><l>大聖力勢不思議</l>
<lb n="0219b02" ed="T"/><l>奉<note n="0219011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">現＝親ィ【原】</note><note n="0219011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">現【大】，親【校異-原】</note><app n="0219011"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">親</rdg></app>一法速超越</l><l>於一法中復現三</l>
<lb n="0219b03" ed="T"/><l>三部各別有三種</l><l>就中最初是攘災</l>
<lb n="0219b04" ed="T"/><l>諸部攘災略說已</l><l>次當增益<note n="0219012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">今＝令【甲】</note><note n="0219012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">今【大】，令【甲】</note><app n="0219012"><lem wit="【大】">今</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">令</rdg></app>說之</l>
<lb n="0219b05" ed="T"/><l>若求長壽及財寶</l><l>復樂聰明聞持門</l>
<lb n="0219b06" ed="T"/><l>或求宿命知前後</l><l>或<note n="0219013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欣＝修【甲】</note><note n="0219013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欣【大】，修【甲】</note><app n="0219013"><lem wit="【大】">欣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">修</rdg></app>現世力如龍</l>
<lb n="0219b07" ed="T"/><l>若為自作增益福</l><l>先須每喫三白食</l>
<lb n="0219b08" ed="T"/><l>若求長壽身無患</l><l>作一火爐蓮華形</l>
<lb n="0219b09" ed="T"/><l>深淺方圓皆一肘</l><l>又取五淨塗其中</l>
<lb n="0219b10" ed="T"/><l>復取蘇密及<note n="0219014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">檀＝檜【甲】</note><note n="0219014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">檀【大】，檜【甲】</note><app n="0219014"><lem wit="【大】">檀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">檜</rdg></app>木</l><l>一呪一燒稱己名</l>
<lb n="0219b11" ed="T"/><l>數至<app type="star" corresp="#0218017"><lem wit="【大】">百八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">八百</rdg></app>一千八</l><l>乃至三千隨<note n="0219015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">前＝所【甲】</note><note n="0219015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前【大】，所【甲】</note><app n="0219015"><lem wit="【大】">前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">所</rdg></app>儀</l>
<lb n="0219b12" ed="T"/><l>若有先世極重業</l><l>不過萬遍悉皆除</l>
<lb n="0219b13" ed="T"/><l>除滅罪已增<note n="0219016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">福＝益ィ【原】</note><note n="0219016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">福【大】，益【校異-原】</note><app n="0219016"><lem wit="【大】">福</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">益</rdg></app>智</l><l>即得無病及命長</l>
<lb n="0219b14" ed="T"/><l>若為他故作此事</l><l>但稱彼名法則同</l>
<lb n="0219b15" ed="T"/><l>行者如法作存心</l><l>每日<note n="0219017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">晨朝＝辰時ィ【原】，晨時【甲】</note><note n="0219017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">晨朝【大】，辰時【校異-原】，晨時【甲】</note><app n="0219017"><lem wit="【大】">晨朝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">辰時</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">晨時</rdg></app>取柳木</l>
<lb n="0219b16" ed="T"/><l>呪滿八百<note n="0219018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＝使ィ【原】</note><note n="0219018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，使【校異-原】</note><app n="0219018"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">使</rdg></app>嚼之</l><l>不久一月或三月</l>
<lb n="0219b17" ed="T"/><l>即能開心得聰明</l><l>作護摩用小心呪</l>
<lb n="0219b18" ed="T"/><l>念誦根本大真言</l><l>我此略說增益福</l>
<lb n="0219b19" ed="T"/><l>無福眾生速加持</l><l>莫<note n="0219019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">論＝福ィ【原】</note><note n="0219019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">論【大】，福【校異-原】</note><app n="0219019"><lem wit="【大】">論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">福</rdg></app>作此數種法</l>
<lb n="0219b20" ed="T"/><l>但願長<note n="0219020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">命＝念【甲】</note><note n="0219020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命【大】，念【甲】</note><app n="0219020"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">念</rdg></app>大護身</l><l>若能每日持千八</l>
<lb n="0219b21" ed="T"/><l>現世即得宿命通</l><l>日夜殷勤恒修<note n="0219021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">習＝集【甲】＊</note><note n="0219021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">習【大】＊，集【甲】＊</note><app n="0219021"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">集</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219b22" ed="T"/><l>所求悉地無不成</l><l>又若服藥求色力</l>
<lb n="0219b23" ed="T"/><l>根本真言加持之</l><l>念誦十萬滿足已</l>
<lb n="0219b24" ed="T"/><l><note n="0219022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔每須…之〕七字－【甲】</note><note n="0219022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（每須…之）七字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="7" n="0219022"><lem wit="【大】">每須空服取服之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></l><l>三七五七復過七</l>
<lb n="0219b25" ed="T"/><l>力同九龍等無差</l><l>若持延年甘露藥</l>
<lb n="0219b26" ed="T"/><l>或得一劫過<note n="0219023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">中劫＝劫中ィ【原】</note><note n="0219023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中劫【大】，劫中【校異-原】</note><app n="0219023"><lem wit="【大】">中劫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">劫中</rdg></app></l><l>若持藥草求成就</l>
<lb n="0219b27" ed="T"/><l>過於諸部以得成</l><l>牛酥雌黃雄黃等</l>
<lb n="0219b28" ed="T"/><l><note n="0219024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">須＝顆ィ【原】</note><note n="0219024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">須【大】，顆【校異-原】</note><app n="0219024"><lem wit="【大】">須</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">顆</rdg></app>持一物置壇中</l><l>白月一日或十五</l>
<lb n="0219b29" ed="T"/><l>初夜起首念誦之</l><l>一期持誦勿間斷</l>
<pb n="0219c" xml:id="T20.1089.0219c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0219c01" ed="T"/><l>及現三相唯限之</l><l>初現煖相成聰智</l>
<lb n="0219c02" ed="T"/><l>第二煙相隱其軀</l><l>第三火現昇空去</l>
<lb n="0219c03" ed="T"/><l>此得成就大仙人</l><l>悉地牛酥應當服</l>
<lb n="0219c04" ed="T"/><l>雄黃等藥用塗之</l><l>我今說此增益訖</l>
<lb n="0219c05" ed="T"/><l>行者努力守護之</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0219c06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="7" type="品">7 隨心憶念品</cb:mulu><head>隨心憶念品第七</head>
<lb n="0219c07" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0219c0701"><l>我今復說隨順<note n="0219025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">事＝等ィ【原】</note><note n="0219025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">事【大】，等【校異-原】</note><app n="0219025"><lem wit="【大】">事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">等</rdg></app></l><l>人與非人及畜生</l>
<lb n="0219c08" ed="T"/><l>又取鹽和大麥<note n="0219026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麫＝麵【甲】＊</note><note n="0219026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麫【大】＊，麵【甲】＊</note><app n="0219026"><lem wit="【大】">麫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">麵</rdg></app></l><l>所求隨心作其形</l>
<lb n="0219c09" ed="T"/><l>男左女右從脚興</l><l>須用<note n="0219027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔賓〕ィ－【原】</note><note n="0219027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賓【大】，〔－〕【校異-原】</note><app n="0219027"><lem wit="【大】">賓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>鐵刀細<note n="0219028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">截＋（之）ィ【原】</note><note n="0219028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">截【大】，截之【校異-原】</note><app n="0219028"><lem wit="【大】">截</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">截之</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219c10" ed="T"/><l>每日三時各百八</l><l>乃至千八自隨心</l>
<lb n="0219c11" ed="T"/><l>若欲羅遮令憶念</l><l>所造形持稱彼名</l>
<lb n="0219c12" ed="T"/><l>護摩亦須念名號</l><l>不過八百即隨心</l>
<lb n="0219c13" ed="T"/><l>若攝諸龍作隨順</l><l>先作一龍似蛇形</l>
<lb n="0219c14" ed="T"/><l>若欲<note n="0219029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">祈＝期【甲】</note><note n="0219029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祈【大】，期【甲】</note><app n="0219029"><lem wit="【大】">祈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">期</rdg></app>雨須青色</l><l>復若澇時應赤色</l>
<lb n="0219c15" ed="T"/><l>燒火須用乳汁木</l><l>不過三日即<note n="0219030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">成＝滅【甲】</note><note n="0219030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成【大】，滅【甲】</note><app n="0219030"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">滅</rdg></app>之</l>
<lb n="0219c16" ed="T"/><l>作法<note n="0219031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">應＝亦【甲】</note><note n="0219031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應【大】，亦【甲】</note><app n="0219031"><lem wit="【大】">應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">亦</rdg></app>須至誠意</l><l>就中不得<note n="0219032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">懈＝晡【甲】</note><note n="0219032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">懈【大】，晡【甲】</note><app n="0219032"><lem wit="【大】">懈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">晡</rdg></app>慢心</l>
<lb n="0219c17" ed="T"/><l>若攝諸天藥叉等</l><l>隨類各各稱本名</l>
<lb n="0219c18" ed="T"/><l>若有怨家令歡喜</l><l>念誦亦得轉彼心</l>
<lb n="0219c19" ed="T"/><l>或作護摩或持誦</l><l>上中下品<note n="0219033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怨家別＝再處之【甲】</note><note n="0219033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怨家別【大】，再處之【甲】</note><app n="0219033"><lem wit="【大】">怨家別</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">再處之</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0219c20" ed="T"/><l>上根福<note n="0219034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">報＝能【甲】</note><note n="0219034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">報【大】，能【甲】</note><app n="0219034"><lem wit="【大】">報</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">能</rdg></app>三百遍</l><l>中下無福再稱之</l>
<lb n="0219c21" ed="T"/><l>隨心念誦我略說</l><l>智者應須諦思惟</l>
<lb n="0219c22" ed="T"/><l>一切部中總攝盡</l><l>祕密最<note n="0219035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">要＝處【甲】</note><note n="0219035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">要【大】，處【甲】</note><app n="0219035"><lem wit="【大】">要</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">處</rdg></app>蓮華心</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0219c23" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="8" type="品">8 阿毘遮嚕迦品</cb:mulu><head>阿毘遮嚕迦品第八</head>
<lb n="0219c24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0219c2401"><l>我今稽首彼大聖</l><l>為現種種方便門</l>
<lb n="0219c25" ed="T"/><l>護佛法故現忿怒</l><l>降伏破滅聖法人</l>
<lb n="0219c26" ed="T"/><l>此中火爐須三角</l><l>用燒雌木兼<note n="0219036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">濕＝溫【甲】＊</note><note n="0219036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">濕【大】＊，溫【甲】＊</note><app n="0219036"><lem wit="【大】">濕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">溫</rdg></app>薪</l>
<lb n="0219c27" ed="T"/><l>若作此法須黑月</l><l>或用一日及月頭</l>
<lb n="0219c28" ed="T"/><l><note n="0219037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">露＝路【甲】</note><note n="0219037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">露【大】，路【甲】</note><app n="0219037"><lem wit="【大】">露</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">路</rdg></app>體<note n="0219038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">樂幽＝叩齒ヵ【原】</note><note n="0219038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">樂幽【大】，叩齒【考偽-原】</note><app n="0219038"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">樂幽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="correctionRemark">叩齒</rdg></app>及忿怒</l><l>大聲持誦稱彼名</l>
<lb n="0219c29" ed="T"/><l>惡酥惡油擲爐<note n="0219039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">底＝舌ィ【原】</note><note n="0219039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">底【大】，舌【校異-原】</note><app n="0219039"><lem wit="【大】">底</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">舌</rdg></app></l><l>不滿千八自然成</l>
<pb n="0220a" xml:id="T20.1089.0220a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0220a01" ed="T"/><l>降伏鬼神卒暴者</l><l>應可復燒禮<note n="0220001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚕＝唱【甲】</note><note n="0220001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚕【大】，唱【甲】</note><app n="0220001"><lem wit="【大】">嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">唱</rdg></app>根</l>
<lb n="0220a02" ed="T"/><l>或燒苦楝或生木</l><l><app type="star" corresp="#0219026"><lem wit="【大】">麫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">麵</rdg></app>和人血復作形</l>
<lb n="0220a03" ed="T"/><l>一截一呪百八遍</l><l>不過三<note n="0220002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">日＝百【甲】</note><note n="0220002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日【大】，百【甲】</note><app n="0220002"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">百</rdg></app>即調柔</l>
<lb n="0220a04" ed="T"/><l>若復降伏滅法者</l><l>加意供養<note n="0220003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝本【甲】</note><note n="0220003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，本【甲】</note><app n="0220003"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">本</rdg></app>明王</l>
<lb n="0220a05" ed="T"/><l>用諸毒藥燒爐<note n="0220004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">中＝裏【甲】</note><note n="0220004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中【大】，裏【甲】</note><app n="0220004"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">裏</rdg></app></l><l>又取<app type="star" corresp="#0219036"><lem wit="【大】">濕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">溫</rdg></app>薪作護摩</l>
<lb n="0220a06" ed="T"/><l>於三日中八百遍</l><l>令彼惡人即迴心</l>
<lb n="0220a07" ed="T"/><l><note n="0220005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">復＝彼【甲】</note><note n="0220005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，彼【甲】</note><app n="0220005"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">彼</rdg></app>若不作護摩事</l><l>持誦根本真言明</l>
<lb n="0220a08" ed="T"/><l>所欲降伏一切者</l><l>句句皆須稱彼名</l>
<lb n="0220a09" ed="T"/><l>其數復滿八百遍</l><l>彼即自來尊敬之</l>
<lb n="0220a10" ed="T"/><l>依法略說此調伏</l><l>行者應須諦思惟</l>
<lb n="0220a11" ed="T"/><l>甚深祕密口<note n="0220006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訣＝決【甲】</note><note n="0220006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訣【大】，決【甲】</note><app n="0220006"><lem wit="【大】">訣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">決</rdg></app>法</l><l>次第念誦都攝門</l>
<lb n="0220a12" ed="T"/><l>若能承<note n="0220007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">侍＝傳ィ【原】</note><note n="0220007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侍【大】，傳【校異-原】</note><app n="0220007"><lem wit="【大】">侍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">傳</rdg></app>此尊者</l><l>不是一生種善根</l>
<lb n="0220a13" ed="T"/><l>曾經無量諸佛所</l><l>修<app type="star" corresp="#0219021"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">集</rdg></app>菩<note n="0220008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">提＝薩【甲】</note><note n="0220008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">提【大】，薩【甲】</note><app n="0220008"><lem wit="【大】">提</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">薩</rdg></app>究竟門</l>
<lb n="0220a14" ed="T"/><l>就中若值善知識</l><l>一生即入不壞門</l>
<lb n="0220a15" ed="T"/><l>我若廣說此功德</l><l>無量億劫<note n="0220009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">歎＝莫【甲】</note><note n="0220009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歎【大】，莫【甲】</note><app n="0220009"><lem wit="【大】">歎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>無窮</l>
<lb n="0220a16" ed="T"/><l>今已略陳此少耳</l><l>行者精心勤修之</l></lg>
<lb n="0220a17" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>都表如意輪儀軌</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>